{"tid":49713,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"肥婆ICON而家即係點?過左海就神仙?","createTime":"2016-12-22T01:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T02:37:05.000Z","uid":18671,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c23833857c92aa6d606164f60f9038800fa70c5f","tid":49713,"uid":18671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T01:59:04.000Z","msg":"呢幾日大把人屌<br />\n眾巴打羅列左一堆理由點解今次肥婆ICON係咁多人反對<br />\n我唔重覆<br />\n加上<br />\n二千幾人負評<br />\n你唔係打算加個垃圾自訂過瀘就算數呀嘛?<br />\n千幾人正評上架<br />\n二千幾人評唔係唔收佢皮呀嘛<br />\n今次柒左咪認囉<br />\n<br />\nBTW 撐肥婆個班,入黎唔好講埋D咩 做得好辛苦好比心機,尊重創作,你唔想睇可以死返高登呢D垃圾理由,呢幾日講撚到口臭屌你老母"},{"pid":"1cbf592c3f3d3fb07625de6363fa450fe036a724","tid":49713,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:01:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5fc397982d8f1b1b566c2e0d13832e219d68159","tid":49713,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc <br />\n<br />\n如果你行出街有二千幾人覺得你樣衰<br />\n<br />\n你係唔係以後唔出街？"},{"pid":"f60cfa680b642dc754335715c0466ef28edd2a60","tid":49713,"uid":52763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:02:16.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"bdae994a96de5079810465242ad01a010a81aec4","tid":49713,"uid":11880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:03:17.000Z","msg":"條肥婆又死出黎辣火頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7403a6aaa2b260c094978b87735596c57618a8ab","tid":49713,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:03:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5677dc41a816f73ff57f2a53167add5fdbca3b7","tid":49713,"uid":27017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T